{"tid":1794610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和你Shop公佈成績單：大陸遊客大減7成","createTime":"2019-12-23T08:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T10:13:17.000Z","uid":20689,"like":285,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"b3eb49da79e4cf506c827f74aaf03c978b49fc8c","tid":1794610,"uid":20689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:51:00.000Z","msg":"記住：<br />\n<br />\n光復香港係一個緩慢過程，由經濟、文化、民生、政治上慢慢脫離/除去大陸化，最後係各領域都光復香港<br />\n<br />\n- 減少大陸遊客能夠重塑香港旅遊業，將藥房、金行等依靠中國人生意，將此一大香港惡性腫瘤除去<br />\n<br />\n- 重新吸納有質素外地遊客，並發展立足香港，面向世界的旅遊業和經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n- 最後降低中國人對香港經濟的限制和影響，達到經濟上光復香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/11Cyrwz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F11Cyrwz.png&h=5d695239&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後加上教學，如何有智慧地趕走大陸旅客？<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>支那人好賤格 人邊話唔黎 一邊身體燈好誠實 買安全套都要落黎買先至有信心<br />\n<br />\n咁點先令到佢地唔落黎呢？<br />\n<br />\n你屌佢 佢表面好介意 但實際上忍住比你地屌都照落黎 所以成效不大 <br />\n<br />\n咁點先得呢？<br />\n<br />\n重點就係，<span style=\"color: red;\">逼中國政府唔批自遊行/旅行團/1日遊落黎</span><br />\n<br />\n咁點先得？好簡單<br />\n<br />\n中共最驚就係中間人落黎「學壞」<br />\n<br />\n只要我地目標<span style=\"color: red;\">做到「教壞支那遊客」既現象</span> <br />\n<br />\n咁自然中共就唔會比佢地落黎香港<br />\n<br />\n試諗下 係sogo 門口/ 廣東道 我地整條流動人鏈 <br />\n<br />\n舉住「親 廣州人為了自身權利起來反抗了 燒警車 打公安 你呢？」<br />\n<br />\n「燒警車 打公安 結果就能爭取維權了 你學到了嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n一邊舉住廣州人玩炮仗 燒警車既相 <br />\n<br />\n一邊唱榮光 <br />\n<br />\n你估中共會唔會比深圳人/廣州人落黎一日自遊行？<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">條街無曬大陸人真係好爽呀</span></span>！"},{"pid":"2f0136b10dad372f327f7c72dd646a32ea8aace2","tid":1794610,"uid":20689,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:53:58.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<br />\n依個算係送比香港人聖誕禮物"},{"pid":"0defca5a4a0fc3d93cb3330e0207499f8306a094","tid":1794610,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b9377b22f012679523e42f134dfada0088fe70","tid":1794610,"uid":223244,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:56:35.000Z","msg":"D 大陸人湧哂去上水"},{"pid":"eb7a64393de69e17bd4550de6f2969960f6f996e","tid":1794610,"uid":243677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:57:31.000Z","msg":"比心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f54dfa67346dde7f61881323753fec08507f6c","tid":1794610,"uid":21920,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"78b9377b22f012679523e42f134dfada0088fe70","tid":1794610,"uid":223244,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:56:35.000Z","msg":"D 大陸人湧哂去上水"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:57:32.000Z","msg":"上水都唔係好多大陸客嫁炸"},{"pid":"f2440999bb23a50ebe98ac0c421172896c94255d","tid":1794610,"uid":69334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:58:01.000Z","msg":"繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-----------------<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a39c188d8c1e884dea38cb44355c8bb681743c1","tid":1794610,"uid":132710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:58:03.000Z","msg":"光復上水！"},{"pid":"5062bff317da7acc76b06d44beb552e90b977a94","tid":1794610,"uid":171259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:58:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"h