a16fd3f2866ba71a9148d4cfa","tid":1794610,"uid":237517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T05:45:07.000Z","msg":"但灣仔d乞衣又出返黎"},{"pid":"f15401b729d699f25117e48f3e26560e08c549f9","tid":1794610,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T05:57:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>SHOP商場戰略檢討與重點</ins></strong></span> 幫手share<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><strong>1) 落閘就目標已達成, 可以轉場</strong></ins></span><br />\n商場落閘基本上都係因為D狗入撚哂黎, 咁達成目標 無需要再屌狗同戀戰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>2) 街坊被捕個時麻煩街坊咪撚係度嘈</ins></strong></span><br />\n琴日已經有幾次係因為街坊太嘈, 個街坊大聲叫都無人聽到佢講乜, 咁樣同害9自己友無分別。一陣無名無姓無資料, 係咪想人地被消失??<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>3) 回馬槍，D狗走個時唔撚好再上前</ins></strong></span><br />\n尤其是商場入面，例如琴日ＹＯＨＯ已經比人回馬槍左起碼3-4次。每次都捉撚左2-3個。屌狗還屌狗, 你地係後面屌就爽, 企前面既街坊就中伏。唔好再做豬隊友<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>4) 12點好撤，再留係度攬炒指數低</ins></strong></span><br />\n咁夜對政權既傷害係邊度? 個撚個都返鳩哂屋企訓教, 車又少。同玩平原戰 自殺有咩分別? 大家要記住個目標係乜野。街上又無其他路人幫你地cover, 過左12點又無車走。好似琴日MK咁, D人又話走唔撚到比狗包圍住。咁唔該你地今日咪撚再要呀寶出動"},{"pid":"5afb2afa942e4f1436cf0f0a175839e06c983683","tid":1794610,"uid":2837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T06:08:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1dcd9150411664dca88916a470fbf4ba4d0fe85e","tid":1794610,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T06:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65beb74291cfa3c248b0e578c75a01baa2728b37","tid":1794610,"uid":20689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94e58e542c3b2c4c372ca366b42362586f5e613c","tid":1794610,"uid":223256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T05:43:09.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\